Rating: 4
Yum! This took all of fifteen minutes to make and it was wonderful! I served it at dinner with four of my girlfriends, and we finished the entire thing; I plan on making it again this weekend to take to a party. I bought a frozen unbaked pie shell in a pan (the ones from Whole Foods are delicious), so that made things even simpler.

